{"lemma":"عَمَلُ","slug":"عَمَلُ","root":"ع.م.ل","root_slug":"ع-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَمَل","root":"عمل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":71},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":18},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30565","n30573","n30574"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to work, perform","tags":["intransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"هُوَ يَعْمَلُ فِي مَجَالِ التَكْنُولُوجِيَا.","english":"He works in the field of technology."},{"text":"أَنَا أَعْمَلُ مُدَرِّسًا فِي الْمَدْرَسَةِ.","english":"I work as a teacher at the school."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to do (with deliberate thought)","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"إِنَّ اللَّهَ يُدْخِلُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ جَنَّاتٍ تَجْرِي مِن تَحْتِهَا الْأَنْهَارُ","english":"Allah will surely admit those who believe and do good into Gardens, under which rivers flow"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to practice, profess"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to produce an effect"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be brisk, walk fast"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to exercise an influence"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to govern a case","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to take pains (عَلَى (ʕalā) with)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to work to an end"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to take care of"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to last without interruption"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pay (someone) their fee or wages"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make (someone) an administrator or governor"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to suppurate, grow cancerous"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَمِلَ (ʕamila) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"action, act, deed"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"work, business","examples":[{"text":"الْعَمَلُ الْجَمَاعِيُّ يُمْكِنُ أَن يَكُونَ مُفِيدًا فِي إِنْجَازِ الْمُشَارِيعِ الْكَبِيرَةِ.","english":"Collaborative work can be beneficial in completing large projects."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"government"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"The grammatical “government” meaning is a semantic loan from Medieval Latin vīs. Compare Hebrew עָמָל (`Amal, “work, deed”)."},"ipa":["/ʕa.mi.la/","/ʕam.ma.la/","/ʕa.mal/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30565","headword_ar":"عَمِلَ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He worked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrought; laboured; served,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did service: he did, acted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"performed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [generally,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a sort of difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with intention;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but sometimes said of an inanimate thing: (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below:)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made, wrought, manufactured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constructed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing. (Msb. [See, again,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.]) Accord. to Az,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamila","text_ar":"عَمِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the only trans. verb of its measure having the inf. n. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalN","text_ar":"فَعَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", except"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"habilat","text_ar":"هَبِلَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a mother, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"habalN","text_ar":"هَبَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; other similar verbs having the inf. n. of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolN","text_ar":"فَعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariTotu All~uqomapa","text_ar":"سَرِطْتُ اللُّقْمَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroTN","text_ar":"سَرْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baliEotuhu","text_ar":"بَلِعْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baloEN","text_ar":"بَلْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA. [But see arts."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"srT","text_ar":"سرط"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blE","text_ar":"بلع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; with respect to the former of which I must here state that, since it was printed, I have found an authority for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroTN","text_ar":"سَرْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariTa","text_ar":"سَرِطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a copy of the S; though in the K it is said to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHar~akap","text_ar":"مُحَرَّكَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and accord. to the Msb it is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEabN","text_ar":"تَعَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamilotu EalaY AlS~adaqapi","text_ar":"عَمِلْتُ عَلَى الصَّدَقَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I officiated in the collecting of the poor-rate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamila bimaA fiY kitaAbi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"عَمِلَ بِمَا فِى كِتَابِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did according to what is"},{"kind":"text","text":"enjoined"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the Book of God."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamila fiY halaAkihi","text_ar":"عَمِلَ فِى هَلَاكِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He laboured to destroy him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to kill him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$yT","text_ar":"شيط"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamila fiyhi","text_ar":"عَمِلَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It acted upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and, said of a sword &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it had effect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made an impression, upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamila fiyhi","text_ar":"عَمِلَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It governed it syntactically;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused"},{"kind":"text","text":"it to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marofuwE","text_ar":"مَرْفُوع"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoSuwb","text_ar":"مَنْصُوب"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majoruwr","text_ar":"مَجْرُور"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it produced in it a certain species of syntactical desinence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamila Albaroqu","text_ar":"عَمِلَ البَرْقُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lightning was continual."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamilato biA^u*unayohaA","text_ar":"عَمِلَتْ بِاُذُنَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a she-camel, (K,) and also, in a trad., of [the beast]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlburaAq","text_ar":"البُرَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She went quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swiftly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) because she that does thus puts her ears in motion by reason of the vehemence of the pace. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamilat","text_ar":"عَمِلَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone] said of a she-camel, signifies [the same: or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, brisk, light, active,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b4-  And [hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamo A^ara Aln~afaqapa taEomalu kamaA taEomalu bimak~apa","text_ar":"لَمْ اَرَ النَّفَقَةَ تَعْمَلُ كَمَا تَعْمَلُ بِمَكَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a saying mentioned by Lh, is expl. by ISd as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanofaqu","text_ar":"تَنْفَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not seen the money that that one expends pass away as it passes away in Mekkeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n30573","headword_ar":"عَمَلٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned in the beginning of this art. as an inf. n.] is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miahonapN","text_ar":"مَِهْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2159},{"kind":"text","text":"[accordingly, when used as a simple subst., it may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Work, labour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"service:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a deed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or it has a more particular meaning than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEol","text_ar":"فِعْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a sort of difficulty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and therefore it is not attributed to God: or, accord. to Er-Rághib, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEol","text_ar":"فِعْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"action"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that proceeds from an animate being by his intention;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and thus it has a more particular meaning than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fEl","text_ar":"فعل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is sometimes attributed to animate beings from which it proceeds without intention; and sometimes to inanimate things, to which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamal","text_ar":"عَمَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is seldom attributed; and this is not used in relation to [irrational] animals except [as implied] in the phrases"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibilN EawaAmilu","text_ar":"اـِبِلٌ عَوَامِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baqarN EawaAmilu","text_ar":"بَقَرٌ عَوَامِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, accord. to MF, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamal","text_ar":"عَمَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a motion of the whole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a portion, of the body;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the mind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the utterance of a saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as well as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the doing a deed with the member,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limb, with which things are gained"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earned;"},{"kind":"text","text":"though most readily understood as applied particularly to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the latter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some apply it particularly to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which is not a saying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is also said that a saying is not termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the common conventional language: and the truth is said to be, that it is not included in the terms"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"otherwise than tropically: (TA:) [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamilapN","text_ar":"عَمِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[used as a simple subst.] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEomaAlN","text_ar":"اَعْمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) In the following saying, of a woman dandling her child, (S,) or of Keys Ibn-Ásim, (O, TA,) dandling his child Hakeem, (TA,)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A^a$obiho A^abaA A^um~ika A^awo A^a$obiho Eamalo"},{"kind":"text","text":"the last word is a proper name of a man: (S, O, TA:) or, accord. to Aboo-Zekereeyà, [the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Share thou in the qualities of the father of thy mother,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"share thou in the qualities of my course of action;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for he says that] by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamalo","text_ar":"عَمَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here meant"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamaliY","text_ar":"عَمَلِى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aibonu EamaliY","text_ar":"اِبْنُ عَمَلِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who does my work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like of what I do."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bnY","text_ar":"بنى"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN A@bonu EamalK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ ا@بْنُ عَمَلٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is strong."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banuw EamalK","text_ar":"بَنُو عَمَلٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Those who journey on foot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, * TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamalu Aln~axoli","text_ar":"عَمَلُ النَّخْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in the T, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DayoEapN","text_ar":"ضَيْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The culture of palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamalu AlA^roDi","text_ar":"عَمَلُ الارْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agriculture"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"striving, labouring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"toiling, in work;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"holding on,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"continuing, in work:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the saying of El- Kutámee"},{"kind":"quote","text":"faqado yahuwnu EalaY AlmusotanojiHi AlEamalu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"For verily the striving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in work is a light matter to him who seeks success"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An office of administration;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"office of governor of a province;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"office of collector of the poor-rates,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an agency of any kind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"management of the affairs and property of another; an employment."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A province;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"territory under a governor appointed by a sovereign."},{"kind":"text","text":"Pl. in this and other senses as above.]"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","O"]},{"entry_id":"n30574","headword_ar":"عَمِلٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", as an epithet applied to a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw","text_ar":"ذُو"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalK","text_ar":"عَمَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having work, labour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"service"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Sb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamuwlN","text_ar":"عَمُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adapted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposed, by nature, to work, labour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"service;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamuwlN","text_ar":"عَمُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, * O, * K:) or this latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that makes much gain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And, applied to lightning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Continuing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"continual."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamilapN","text_ar":"عَمِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a she-camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Brisk, light, active,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) like ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEomalapN","text_ar":"يَعْمَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eam~aAlapN","text_ar":"عَمَّالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]}]}}